e":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:54:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cbD7ezv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcbD7ezv.png&h=bc78b559&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D8hzD1c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD8hzD1c.png&h=efe03efc&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:56:45.000Z","msg":"屌你咪屌你囉<br />\n點撚樣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPRHNX6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPRHNX6.png&h=86eb5756&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qVRgSpM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqVRgSpM.png&h=4f9b68d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7TcWSpO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7TcWSpO.png&h=737f57d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NrCf7X9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNrCf7X9.png&h=5e12dc7a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d051fcf3889815abf694b76cb43dea625c44863","tid":1475382,"uid":140326,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:08:33.000Z","msg":"【杜絕分化】熱狗惡行 24小時輪流廣播 （2）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dfHFHS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dfHFHS</a><br />\n<br />\n陳雲熱狗支持者聽住；<br />\n<br />\n前線已經有曬共識被攻擊會還擊，左膠無左好耐<br />\n當年佔中<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">除左督灰外</span></span>，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">熱狗分化撚日日屌3屌4</span></span><br />\n屌 泛民/本土/天琦/左膠/大台/港豬<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌到部分香港人心灰意冷</span></span><br />\n都有份<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">破壞整個運動</span>，<br />\n廢老黃毓民而家仲日日叫泛民總辭，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人地泛民都醒水</span></span>無督灰，<br />\n年輕議員仲上前線幫手，<br />\n熱狗4年之後<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲用番果幾招分化</span></span> 唔悶架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然到而家都無見到陳雲，毓民 都係冷氣軍師，<br />\n但如果文章無屌 泛民/本土/天琦/梁繼平/左膠/大台/冷氣軍師 （基本上全部都屌過）<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">講野合理都會聽下</span></span>，<br />\n自從上次選舉比大陸朱踢爆左係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中共白手套</span></span>，<br />\n每次睇佢地講野都會<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警惕有無字裹行間分化</span></span>"},{"pid":"987d7e9774fb35771ded04e3c4aadd88d5eea75b","tid":1475382,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:38:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89130511e689fb0b128341fc3f7394c5b226d642","tid":1475382,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:39:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb677bc4e5fb187124f6e85d0900df557c17939c","tid":1475382,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:45:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}